    "gp_section_612362157874479981": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "8e03a11685fceead31cb6d12ac5e5a0ce9931f92cbfeccbd1cc8d454f1094fd1_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg0eIFnCAo5_text": "<p>Loaded with vitamins and antioxidants to protect and moisturize.</p>",
        "gg2T0Kooql6_text": "<p>Never used tallow soap before, so I ordered the sample pack to see how it was. After one use, I went right back to the website and ordered a 5 pack. The way the soap makes your skin feel nourished is incredible. All the scents smell amazing and each bar lasts a long time. Threw out all of my other body wash products once I used Health Y Sol. Never going back!\"</p>",
        "gg72ZxZb2zr_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/4d0f7f4c-146e-4e36-8abd-2c2c5054508b.webp",
        "ggA-_hPo_Dv_childItem_0": "<p>70k+ Happy Customers</p>",
