        "ggAqq_boREA_text": "This Is What Clean Should Look Like",
        "ggB6yBe5BJi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/336b7a3c-fe95-44d2-8605-e23ba8aa1b65.webp",
        "ggGBJvmZNCy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_9zoljm9zoljm9zol.png",
        "ggGVcHhhEJt_text": "Organic Essential Oils",
        "ggGc9QlfvXH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/a119973c-3510-4692-b2d5-0b62da0fc242.webp",
        "ggHhSMo0QnN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/b92924d9-1f0e-4df4-a1c8-7ac59c111163.webp",
        "ggI5oeMmafn_text": "<p>Pure plant extracts for scent and skin support, no fake fragrances.</p>",
        "ggMJuONVxs8_text": "Bone Marrow",
        "ggNHFaUcLAW_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggP2ceTRk60_text": "<p>See why thousands switched — 10% OFF + Free Soap ends soon</p>",
        "ggQ2rT5UD3Z_text": "Shea Butter",
        "ggQz2Dravka_text": "<p>ABBY B.</p>",
        "ggRY952yK2D_text": "Organic Herbal Infusions",
        "ggU2lOn0nmL_label": "<p>Shop bow</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggV5XnARgcv_text": "Raw Honey",
        "ggWpT6Dac3C_childItem_0": "<p>Lifetime Guarantee</p>",
        "ggXWZuBARA2_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggXcJKgwwaT_text": "<p>MSHER</p>",
        "ggXyvIXjGu0_text": "<p>Natural antibacterial and moisture magnet for soft, protected skin.</p>",
        "ggY8C-UX2q1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/eea45b39-ba5b-429e-8fba-6383fea5538d.webp",
        "ggYh8FrRQPu_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "gg_GolCVIYb_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_7otqku7otqku7otq.png",
        "ggaGKB2skJ3_text": "<p>Every bar, balm, and bottle is made with natural, healing ingredients — nothing synthetic, nothing hidden.</p>",
        "gge8IRBL8ws_childItem_0": "<p>Lifetime Guarantee</p>",
        "ggfu0fa1yPo_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_85q9eo85q9eo85q9.png",
        "ggg3RjJhELR_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggh4HuXuztW_text": "<p>THE BEST Tallow soap I’ve tried This is by far THE BEST Tallow soap I’ve tried. It leaves you soooo soft, the scents are perfect, not too strong and not weak. I will definitely be repurchasing the bundle once I run out. Highly recommend!</p>",
        "gghXKPetwgi_text": "<p>Rich in natural collagen and skin-identical lipids that deeply nourish, strengthen, and support skin repair.</p>",
        "ggidu3t0JhP_text": "Only <span style=\"color:#F15722;\">ingredients </span>your skin recognizes",
        "ggif1nKajVq_childItem_0": "<p>70k+ Happy Customers</p>",
        "ggivuCOmRLC_text": "Grass-Fed Tallow",
        "ggj_Gps3oMy_text": "<p>SHELLEY</p>",
        "ggjt39Ospck_text": "Organic Olive &amp; Coconut Oils",
        "gglAFXqPeI2_label": "<p>Shop bow</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "gglrGsWYdhC_text": "<p>Melissa</p>",
        "ggmcQa9tK54_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_cfd1zncfd1zncfd1.png",
        "ggmmRg7Zxv1_childItem_0": "<p>Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggo19-FRmf__text": "<p>Packed with essential fatty acids and vitamins A, D, E &amp; K to moisturize, protect, and mimic your skin’s natural barrier.</p>",
        "ggpGcVlKzxg_text": "<p>Best soap I’ve ever used! Been a faithful dr. Squatch guy for a couple years but after getting on carnivore diet and seeing health benefits of natural animal products I was won over ny their small business model, appreciation and goal for natural health and being a conservative. After using this soap the smell stays so long on the skin throighout the day feeling fresh and my skin is so much smoother after just 2 uses.</p>",
        "ggrQFmyUYPe_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/5f764bcb-16e6-4adf-9f33-50a554dcd17c.webp",
        "ggs9dZn8OIL_text": "<p>A little goes a long way. It goes into the skin very nicely and does not irritate it at all. I will be using this all summer long, and don't mind applying it daily because it moisturizes and makes my skin look good. Great sun protecting product!</p>",
        "ggsUEOCeKQv_text": "<p>Deeply nourishing natural fat rich in vitamins A &amp; E that hydrates, softens, and protects dry or damaged skin while strengthening the skin barrier.</p>",
        "ggumCEb2OXf_text": "<p>Shortly after I received this balm, I spilled boiling water on my arm, After cooling with cold water I used the balm. The pain and redness receded pretty fast. It has helped with healing tremendously. Amazing stuff. Thank you!</p>",
        "ggxihK7VoeW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_q3sww7q3sww7q3sw.png",
        "ggzKbwe4ceu_text": "<p>Chamomile, arnica, calm inflammation and speed recovery.</p>",
        "ggzPh13_LMH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_961ahv961ahv961a_1.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-612362157874479981"
    },
    "gp_section_612388973536346923": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "00fe6863d01748262809bbfade4a2141843af83d064e0d447fa99d62cec0b45e_1_1_1_0__1",
