    "gp_section_612389338625344299": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "0f7b21bdb29277443a0ddab86e5b07f9aa188cad217bf9858b4a15c0ba2c2cc3_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg8i6PzUgOe_text": "<p>Our bar soap is an excellent choice for babies. Our soap is mostly tallow which is perfect for sensitive skin. We recommend using our unscented variation as some babies might be sensitive to essential oils.</p>",
        "ggC45EVc6Bw_text": "<p>Many of our customers will notice our soap bars are not only larger than most others, but they last longer too. With proper care, you can expect your bar of soap to last 6-8 weeks.</p>",
        "ggF01h_EDti_label": "<p>Shop bow</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggKLbG-d1ji_text": "<p>Absolutely. It is safe for sensitive skin like on the face and for kids and babies.</p>",
        "ggM5I9NPv5q_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggNI_JcU2I-_childItem_0": "<p>70k+ Happy Customers</p>",
        "ggbuBKym1a9_text": "<p>No worries, we offer a customer satisfaction guarantee.</p>",
        "gghFxDx_LgN_childItem_0": "<p>Lifetime Guarantee</p>",
        "ggljbLDxZCu_text": "<p>Most of the time skin issues are related to your diet and gut health. For this reason we cannot guarantee that our soap will heal your skin. But we have had dozens of customers report back to us with improved skin conditions! Sometimes you are a simple soap swap away from your best skin. Like our founder. About Us</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_0": "<p>Is your soap safe for sensitive skin and conditions like eczema or rosacea?</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_1": "<p>Will this help clear my acne or improve my skin?</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_2": "<p>What makes your soap different from other “natural” brands?</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_3": "<p>Is this really worth the price?</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_4": "<p>Can I use this on my face (or on kids)?</p>",
        "ggpXWvQkHup_childItem_5": "<p>What if I don’t like it?</p>",
        "ggvFtfTkF5T_text": "<p>While most other brands rely on cheap oils that waste away quickly in a soap bar, we use beef tallow which creates a very hard, long lasting bar. It’s also a much more sustainable option compared to palm oil. Additionally, we only use organic essential oils for fragrance, whereas most other soap companies are using synthetic fragrances that are harming your health.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-612389338625344299"
    },
    "gp_section_612390896238854955": {
